<SYNC Start=1896255><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1897528><P Class=KRCC>
- 바꾼다고?<br>
- 응
<SYNC Start=1900053><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1902901><P Class=KRCC>
그래, 왜?
<SYNC Start=1904960><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1905003><P Class=KRCC>
별로인 것 같아서...
<SYNC Start=1909463><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1909507><P Class=KRCC>
